This map was created originally by Cleav420

This is #5 map i have made.


I have made more towers with more rooms and props on top of them.
Tons Glass ramps some glass in map brakeable.
Hideing spots around cargo areas. There is even two towers with water inside to swim up to the top.
A hella of lot of ladders spread out to get up to towers.

I will be working on v3 as soon as i learn a few more things about mapping.

please leave any info on how the map need to be for v3.
